WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.990
Good morning, everybody. I just wanted

00:00:03.000 --> 00:00:05.210
to come on and tell you all a word

00:00:05.220 --> 00:00:07.070
that the Lord has for you today. I just

00:00:07.080 --> 00:00:08.990
want to introduce my son, Braden.

00:00:09.000 --> 00:00:11.270
'Hey, what's up? I'm the editor

00:00:11.280 --> 00:00:13.850
for 90% of his

00:00:13.860 --> 00:00:15.770
videos. I edit the shorts. You guys are

00:00:15.770 --> 00:00:15.780
being

00:00:15.780 --> 00:00:16.790
nice to me in the comments;

00:00:16.800 --> 00:00:17.990
you're all asking, 'Who's the

00:00:17.990 --> 00:00:18.000
editor?'and

00:00:18.000 --> 00:00:20.990
it was me.'The Lord's really gifted

00:00:21.000 --> 00:00:22.670
him, and he's trying really hard.

00:00:22.680 --> 00:00:24.170
'Yeah, I try to make them match. I try to do

00:00:24.180 --> 00:00:26.750
the math and stuff. It's a

00:00:26.760 --> 00:00:28.370
lot of work, but I hope you all enjoy it; it's

00:00:28.370 --> 00:00:28.380
fun.'He's

00:00:28.380 --> 00:00:31.009
15 years old. 'Yeah, I try to

00:00:31.019 --> 00:00:32.510
make the shorts,

00:00:32.520 --> 00:00:34.790
try to pick the topics and stuff. So if

00:00:34.800 --> 00:00:36.530
you guys have any ideas for shorts, just

00:00:36.540 --> 00:00:38.090
let me know down in the comments so I

00:00:38.100 --> 00:00:39.830
can make some better shorts because

00:00:39.840 --> 00:00:41.389
everybody seems to really like the end-time

00:00:41.389 --> 00:00:41.399
stuff—what's

00:00:41.399 --> 00:00:43.010
going to happen

00:00:43.020 --> 00:00:44.990
and what we're fixing to head

00:00:44.990 --> 00:00:45.000
into.'This

00:00:45.000 --> 00:00:47.389
is my

00:00:47.389 --> 00:00:47.399
son

00:00:47.399 --> 00:00:49.190
right here;

00:00:49.200 --> 00:00:50.810
I'm really proud of him. He works really

00:00:50.820 --> 00:00:52.850
hard, he's really smart, he does

00:00:52.850 --> 00:00:52.860
well

00:00:52.860 --> 00:00:55.729
at school, and he loves Jesus with

00:00:55.739 --> 00:00:58.310
all his heart. 'Yeah, I try really

00:00:58.320 --> 00:01:00.889
hard. I have a good upcoming short soon; I'm

00:01:00.899 --> 00:01:02.450
making it right now.'Oh, praise the Lord!

00:01:02.460 --> 00:01:04.609
I just wanted to

00:01:04.619 --> 00:01:06.469
bring him on here and show him

00:01:06.479 --> 00:01:08.149
off. I'm really proud of him and just

00:01:08.159 --> 00:01:11.330
tell people that he loves Jesus.

00:01:11.340 --> 00:01:14.450
I'm going to bring each one

00:01:14.460 --> 00:01:16.429
of my children on and introduce

00:01:16.439 --> 00:01:19.250
them to you all. This is the day I

00:01:19.260 --> 00:01:21.670
told him I wanted to introduce

00:01:24.540 --> 00:01:26.810
the man behind the camera. He's

00:01:26.820 --> 00:01:29.870
my prayer; he prays with me. He sits

00:01:29.880 --> 00:01:32.330
with me every night and we intercede, and

00:01:32.340 --> 00:01:33.770
I'm teaching him how to intercede

00:01:33.770 --> 00:01:33.780
and

00:01:33.780 --> 00:01:37.069
dip in those rivers. He's

00:01:37.079 --> 00:01:39.230
learned a lot. We take communion. He

00:01:39.230 --> 00:01:39.240
was

00:01:39.240 --> 00:01:40.969
there whenever we raised the dog from the

00:01:40.979 --> 00:01:44.149
dead. He was there whenever I

00:01:44.159 --> 00:01:45.710
squashed the dog to death by accident.

00:01:45.720 --> 00:01:48.429
Yeah, it was by accident.

00:01:48.439 --> 00:01:50.749
My wife's behind the camera right now;

00:01:52.220 --> 00:01:56.330
she's holding the camera. If

00:01:56.340 --> 00:01:57.889
you haven't seen that video, we'll link

00:01:57.899 --> 00:01:59.870
it in the description. God raised

00:01:59.880 --> 00:02:01.310
that dog from the dead; it was

00:02:01.320 --> 00:02:02.690
special. Ever since he was a little

00:02:02.700 --> 00:02:05.749
baby boy in diapers, I've been

00:02:05.759 --> 00:02:06.950
teaching him. He's

00:02:06.960 --> 00:02:08.270
been baptized in the Holy Ghost and

00:02:08.280 --> 00:02:09.949
speaking in tongues since he was five

00:02:09.959 --> 00:02:13.190
years old. He sees in the spirit

00:02:13.200 --> 00:02:15.290
too, and the Lord shows him things

00:02:15.290 --> 00:02:15.300
in

00:02:15.300 --> 00:02:17.449
dreams. It's the

00:02:17.459 --> 00:02:19.130
same with my daughter, and you'll meet

00:02:19.140 --> 00:02:21.710
her, probably in the next video—our youngest

00:02:21.720 --> 00:02:23.809
daughter. Family is important

00:02:23.809 --> 00:02:23.819
to me, and

00:02:23.819 --> 00:02:26.030
I just wanted to

00:02:27.900 --> 00:02:30.050
show you all my son and

00:02:30.060 --> 00:02:32.750
introduce you. He's

00:02:32.760 --> 00:02:39.110
a real blessing. Okay,

00:02:39.120 --> 00:02:42.650
about the spirit of forebodings

00:02:42.660 --> 00:02:45.290
and being in intercessory prayer.

00:02:45.300 --> 00:02:47.449
This is very important that you

00:02:47.459 --> 00:02:49.070
hear this because there are a lot of times

00:02:49.080 --> 00:02:51.650
you can feel that heaviness—you feel

00:02:51.660 --> 00:02:54.410
that urge to intercede and

00:02:54.420 --> 00:02:55.970
you're in the moment and you're like, 'Man,

00:02:55.980 --> 00:02:58.369
I feel like there's a weight in the

00:02:58.379 --> 00:02:59.990
spirit realm on

00:02:59.990 --> 00:03:00.000
you.'What

00:03:00.000 --> 00:03:03.710
happens is the demonic tries

00:03:03.720 --> 00:03:07.670
to imitate the spiritual realm, and

00:03:07.680 --> 00:03:09.589
the devil tries to push you into

00:03:09.589 --> 00:03:09.599
things—push,

00:03:09.599 --> 00:03:11.809
push, push.

00:03:11.819 --> 00:03:13.670
This is one of the instances

00:03:13.670 --> 00:03:13.680
of

00:03:13.680 --> 00:03:15.530
what I'm trying to tell you:

00:03:15.540 --> 00:03:17.449
you can walk around and always have a

00:03:17.459 --> 00:03:18.589
spirit of heaviness. It's like a

00:03:18.599 --> 00:03:20.690
heaviness on you. You think, 'Well, it's the

00:03:20.700 --> 00:03:22.790
Lord and the burden to

00:03:22.790 --> 00:03:22.800
pray.'No,

00:03:22.800 --> 00:03:26.089
it's not. There's a spirit of

00:03:26.099 --> 00:03:28.670
forebodings and it tries to come on and

00:03:28.680 --> 00:03:31.130
push you into that place to

00:03:31.140 --> 00:03:33.949
make you not live in a state of joy.

00:03:33.959 --> 00:03:36.710
The fruit of the Spirit is love,

00:03:36.720 --> 00:03:39.649
joy, peace, patience, kindness, goodness,

00:03:39.659 --> 00:03:41.869
gentleness, and self-control. You need to

00:03:41.879 --> 00:03:44.089
understand that when you're not walking

00:03:44.099 --> 00:03:46.309
in that joy, when you're not walking in

00:03:46.319 --> 00:03:47.930
the fruits of the Spirit, there's

00:03:47.940 --> 00:03:50.449
something wrong. To walk in the

00:03:50.459 --> 00:03:52.610
fruits of the Spirit, we have to have the

00:03:52.620 --> 00:03:55.070
preparation of the gospel of peace on

00:03:55.080 --> 00:03:58.070
our feet. If your shoes are not on your

00:03:58.070 --> 00:03:58.080
feet—the

00:03:58.080 --> 00:04:00.050
preparation of the gospel of

00:04:00.050 --> 00:04:00.060
peace—and

00:04:00.060 --> 00:04:02.030
you're not walking in peace,

00:04:02.040 --> 00:04:04.130
you're barefoot and the rest of your

00:04:04.140 --> 00:04:06.890
armor is messed up because you have to

00:04:06.900 --> 00:04:09.289
have good shoes on to walk

00:04:09.299 --> 00:04:11.809
on the serpents and the scorpions with

00:04:11.819 --> 00:04:13.309
the shield of faith. You've got to have

00:04:13.319 --> 00:04:15.050
all those things to quench all the

00:04:15.060 --> 00:04:17.629
fiery darts of the wicked. You need the sword of the Spirit, which is the word of God, to go and cut that devil up. You need to

00:04:17.639 --> 00:04:19.430
be able to have the

00:04:24.120 --> 00:04:26.150
helmet of salvation

00:04:26.160 --> 00:04:27.950
and

00:04:27.960 --> 00:04:29.930
the breastplate of righteousness.

00:04:29.940 --> 00:04:32.030
The spirit of

00:04:32.040 --> 00:04:34.310
forebodings will come and try to

00:04:34.320 --> 00:04:37.249
torment you. You have got to take

00:04:37.259 --> 00:04:40.070
authority over that and make sure that

00:04:40.080 --> 00:04:42.650
whenever you're going into

00:04:42.660 --> 00:04:44.749
intercession, you're not being

00:04:44.759 --> 00:04:47.450
tormented by a spirit of

00:04:47.450 --> 00:04:47.460
forebodings—a

00:04:47.460 --> 00:04:49.670
fearful apprehension, a feeling

00:04:49.670 --> 00:04:49.680
that

00:04:49.680 --> 00:04:51.890
something bad is about to happen.

00:04:51.900 --> 00:04:54.170
You've got to make sure that spirit

00:04:54.180 --> 00:04:56.629
is not pushing you: 'Something bad's about

00:04:56.639 --> 00:04:58.969
to happen, we got to intercede.'We got to

00:04:58.979 --> 00:05:00.710
walk that way. That's the way it was

00:05:00.720 --> 00:05:02.510
for me forever. I had that for years,

00:05:02.520 --> 00:05:04.430
always walking around thinking something

00:05:04.440 --> 00:05:07.010
bad was about to happen. 'Oh no, I feel

00:05:07.020 --> 00:05:09.469
heaviness, it must be...'And when

00:05:09.479 --> 00:05:11.810
the Lord showed me this, He said,

00:05:11.820 --> 00:05:14.210
'Brandon, this is a spirit of

00:05:14.210 --> 00:05:14.220
foreboding

00:05:14.220 --> 00:05:15.950
that's bothering you all the

00:05:15.960 --> 00:05:17.689
time. This isn't a spirit of intercession;

00:05:17.699 --> 00:05:19.610
you need to be able to learn

00:05:19.620 --> 00:05:21.950
the discernment of how to

00:05:21.960 --> 00:05:24.350
divide it.'So I started taking

00:05:24.360 --> 00:05:26.029
authority, and if I start to feel

00:05:26.039 --> 00:05:28.790
that or anything like that, I go, 'Uh-uh. Is

00:05:28.800 --> 00:05:30.590
this a spirit of forebodings, or is this

00:05:30.600 --> 00:05:32.990
the Holy Ghost leading me to start

00:05:33.000 --> 00:05:35.090
interceding for something?'When you

00:05:35.100 --> 00:05:37.129
start binding that spirit back and say,

00:05:37.139 --> 00:05:39.830
'No, I will not yield to a spirit of

00:05:39.840 --> 00:05:41.870
forebodings, but I will yield to the Holy

00:05:41.880 --> 00:05:43.730
Ghost and I will pray in the Holy Ghost

00:05:43.740 --> 00:05:45.950
right now,'I bind any spirit; you're

00:05:45.960 --> 00:05:47.510
not going to torment me because I'm not

00:05:47.520 --> 00:05:49.909
going to walk in torment. Fear

00:05:49.909 --> 00:05:49.919
hath

00:05:49.919 --> 00:05:53.270
torment, but perfect love casteth out all

00:05:53.280 --> 00:05:55.790
fear. You can't allow that to happen

00:05:55.800 --> 00:05:57.469
because I'm telling you, you'll start

00:05:57.479 --> 00:05:58.850
crawling underneath that rock every day,

00:05:58.860 --> 00:06:00.469
and it'll keep leading you

00:06:00.479 --> 00:06:02.090
that way, and you'll live in

00:06:02.100 --> 00:06:03.770
a heaviness and go around like

00:06:03.770 --> 00:06:03.780
Eeyore—you

00:06:03.780 --> 00:06:07.370
know, 'woe is me, everything's

00:06:07.380 --> 00:06:09.950
falling apart.'You can't do that. You've

00:06:09.960 --> 00:06:11.450
got to be the Tigger and

00:06:11.450 --> 00:06:11.460
go,

00:06:11.460 --> 00:06:14.230
'Hey, ha ha, I got

00:06:14.230 --> 00:06:14.240
joy!'I

00:06:14.240 --> 00:06:16.610
hate to use that as an

00:06:16.610 --> 00:06:16.620
illustration,

00:06:16.620 --> 00:06:18.350
y'all, but

00:06:18.360 --> 00:06:19.909
when you have kids, you see Winnie the

00:06:19.919 --> 00:06:22.430
Pooh. Walk in the spirit of joy,

00:06:22.430 --> 00:06:22.440
walk

00:06:22.440 --> 00:06:25.610
in peace, walk in the

00:06:25.620 --> 00:06:27.050
fruits of the Spirit. Another thing I

00:06:27.060 --> 00:06:29.930
need to tell you: the Holy Spirit is a

00:06:29.940 --> 00:06:32.749
person. He's a gentleman, and

00:06:32.759 --> 00:06:35.809
when you invite Him into your life, He

00:06:35.819 --> 00:06:39.590
will... last night

00:06:39.600 --> 00:06:41.390
I was worshiping and He

00:06:41.400 --> 00:06:43.730
said, 'You've dumped out enough

00:06:43.740 --> 00:06:45.710
through these videos. You need to fill

00:06:45.720 --> 00:06:47.870
yourself back up. I need to spend some

00:06:47.880 --> 00:06:49.730
time with you. I need you to separate

00:06:49.740 --> 00:06:52.249
yourself for a while

00:06:52.249 --> 00:06:52.259
now.'Before

00:06:52.259 --> 00:06:53.809
all the videos,

00:06:53.809 --> 00:06:53.819
it

00:06:53.819 --> 00:06:55.790
has been a big

00:06:55.790 --> 00:06:55.800
adjustment

00:06:55.800 --> 00:06:57.469
for me because the time

00:06:57.479 --> 00:06:58.430
that I'm doing these videos

00:06:58.430 --> 00:06:58.440
or

00:06:58.440 --> 00:07:00.290
answering your comments, I used to spend

00:07:00.300 --> 00:07:02.930
in prayer and worship and

00:07:02.940 --> 00:07:04.790
seeking Him. And He said, 'I need you to just

00:07:04.800 --> 00:07:06.350
take your time and separate right now.

00:07:06.360 --> 00:07:08.270
Don't make a video; don't think

00:07:08.280 --> 00:07:10.070
about a video. I need you to dip in the

00:07:10.080 --> 00:07:11.809
river right now. I need you to do this

00:07:11.819 --> 00:07:14.029
for Me.'And I stopped and I said, 'Well,

00:07:14.039 --> 00:07:17.330
okay, Lord.'And the presence of God

00:07:17.340 --> 00:07:18.590
took a little bit, and I

00:07:18.600 --> 00:07:19.550
started getting in there. I started

00:07:19.560 --> 00:07:20.930
singing the song. Like I'm telling y'all,

00:07:20.940 --> 00:07:22.909
I worship Him, and in His presence,

00:07:22.919 --> 00:07:24.830
there's fullness of joy.

00:07:24.840 --> 00:07:25.909
I said,

00:07:25.919 --> 00:07:27.110
'Worship Him,'and I start singing songs

00:07:27.120 --> 00:07:29.990
and I get into His presence. I will enter His gates

00:07:29.990 --> 00:07:30.000
with

00:07:30.000 --> 00:07:31.909
thanksgiving

00:07:31.909 --> 00:07:31.919
in

00:07:31.919 --> 00:07:33.770
my

00:07:33.770 --> 00:07:33.780
heart;

00:07:33.780 --> 00:07:35.689
I enter into those

00:07:35.699 --> 00:07:37.089
courts,

00:07:37.099 --> 00:07:39.770
and I will enter in

00:07:42.240 --> 00:07:45.529
His courts with praise. I will say this

00:07:45.539 --> 00:07:49.909
is the day that the Lord has made. I will

00:07:49.919 --> 00:07:52.730
rejoice and be glad...

00:07:52.740 --> 00:07:55.969
He has made me glad, He has made me glad,

00:07:55.979 --> 00:08:00.529
I will rejoice for He has made me glad.

00:08:00.539 --> 00:08:03.830
You have to get there. You have to

00:08:03.840 --> 00:08:07.610
train yourself to step into that glory

00:08:07.620 --> 00:08:11.210
river, and the more you do it, the easier

00:08:11.220 --> 00:08:13.430
and faster you get there. It's like

00:08:13.440 --> 00:08:15.830
a

00:08:15.840 --> 00:08:17.689
muscle. You keep lifting those spiritual

00:08:17.699 --> 00:08:19.730
weights, you keep working out, and you'll

00:08:19.740 --> 00:08:21.230
start jumping in those rivers really

00:08:21.240 --> 00:08:23.570
quick.

00:08:23.580 --> 00:08:25.909
Honestly, when people say, 'Oh, my prayer

00:08:25.919 --> 00:08:29.089
life is so

00:08:29.099 --> 00:08:29.990
dry,'you've

00:08:30.000 --> 00:08:32.870
got to push

00:08:32.880 --> 00:08:34.850
through those dry times. You don't give

00:08:34.860 --> 00:08:37.790
up. You keep pushing through

00:08:37.800 --> 00:08:38.990
that wall

00:08:40.800 --> 00:08:44.209
by prayer, thanksgiving, and worship.

00:08:46.680 --> 00:08:48.170
When you get through that wall, you'll

00:08:48.180 --> 00:08:49.850
get into the river,

00:08:49.860 --> 00:08:51.710
you'll get in this gusher,

00:08:51.720 --> 00:08:54.050
and

00:08:54.060 --> 00:08:55.850
you'll start getting into that flow so

00:08:55.860 --> 00:08:58.009
strong. And that's whenever He'll

00:08:58.019 --> 00:09:00.290
start taking you places. I'll

00:09:00.300 --> 00:09:02.449
start interceding about things,

00:09:02.459 --> 00:09:04.970
and I'll hear... what's really cool,

00:09:04.970 --> 00:09:04.980
and

00:09:04.980 --> 00:09:07.910
I hope this is kind of

00:09:07.920 --> 00:09:09.829
deep,

00:09:09.839 --> 00:09:11.810
but you all need a little bit of

00:09:11.820 --> 00:09:14.329
deep today. I

00:09:14.339 --> 00:09:16.550
can hear the prayers of the

00:09:16.560 --> 00:09:20.030
intercessors outside. A lot

00:09:20.040 --> 00:09:22.550
of times, I'll go into the spirit and I

00:09:22.560 --> 00:09:25.009
can hear. I listen for this one

00:09:25.019 --> 00:09:27.170
elderly woman—I know she's elderly; I

00:09:28.980 --> 00:09:31.670
assume she's probably in her 80s because

00:09:31.680 --> 00:09:33.829
she knows how to flow

00:09:33.839 --> 00:09:36.530
in the rivers big time—and it's

00:09:36.540 --> 00:09:39.290
almost like a heartbeat. You can start

00:09:39.300 --> 00:09:40.910
going in the spirit realm like a

00:09:40.920 --> 00:09:42.710
heartbeat with people in other parts

00:09:42.720 --> 00:09:46.009
of the world, and you start to sway in,

00:09:46.019 --> 00:09:48.650
and like a fish,

00:09:48.660 --> 00:09:50.690
you're swimming in the stream with them.

00:09:50.700 --> 00:09:52.730
You can start swimming in the stream in

00:09:52.740 --> 00:09:54.790
the spirit with them.

00:09:54.790 --> 00:09:54.800
I

00:09:54.800 --> 00:09:57.470
notice

00:09:57.480 --> 00:10:01.130
these intercessors,

00:10:01.140 --> 00:10:03.470
and the Lord will call me beside them

00:10:03.480 --> 00:10:05.990
even in my own home. I've never met these

00:10:06.000 --> 00:10:07.490
people, but when I get to heaven, I know I

00:10:07.500 --> 00:10:09.590
will. I can go beside them because they

00:10:09.600 --> 00:10:11.090
always pray at a certain time and I

00:10:11.100 --> 00:10:12.710
always pray at certain times,

00:10:12.720 --> 00:10:15.650
and they'll go. But inside me, we'll

00:10:15.660 --> 00:10:18.050
pray and we'll flow in

00:10:18.050 --> 00:10:18.060
the spirit realm

00:10:18.060 --> 00:10:19.670
with them. I can

00:10:19.680 --> 00:10:22.430
feel it, and it's like a

00:10:22.440 --> 00:10:25.070
symphony; it's beautiful music. It's a

00:10:25.080 --> 00:10:26.870
symphony, but we're praying and we're

00:10:26.880 --> 00:10:29.030
bringing down the strongholds,

00:10:29.040 --> 00:10:30.829
setting people

00:10:30.839 --> 00:10:34.130
free and the captives free.

00:10:34.140 --> 00:10:36.710
The spirit realm is more real

00:10:36.720 --> 00:10:39.350
than the natural. I hope you all realize

00:10:39.360 --> 00:10:42.949
the spirit realm is so real.

00:10:42.959 --> 00:10:46.130
It's so amazing what goes on when you

00:10:46.140 --> 00:10:48.290
start tapping into the rivers and you

00:10:48.300 --> 00:10:50.389
start going in with the Holy Ghost and

00:10:50.399 --> 00:10:53.449
flowing with Him in intercessory prayer.

00:10:53.459 --> 00:10:55.490
You'll start to notice people; you'll

00:10:55.500 --> 00:10:57.470
start to notice their heartbeat. You can

00:10:57.480 --> 00:10:59.150
feel them in the spirit realm when

00:10:59.160 --> 00:11:00.530
you're praying. I'm not talking about

00:11:00.540 --> 00:11:01.790
being weird, because some of you

00:11:01.800 --> 00:11:04.310
get really weird, you know, talking

00:11:04.320 --> 00:11:05.630
to angels and doing all that stuff.

00:11:05.640 --> 00:11:07.910
I'm not talking about that. You pray,

00:11:07.920 --> 00:11:12.050
and you can get into some

00:11:12.060 --> 00:11:14.030
really cool stuff in the

00:11:14.040 --> 00:11:15.889
spirit realm when you're praying and you

00:11:15.899 --> 00:11:19.069
grow spiritually. This is

00:11:19.079 --> 00:11:20.870
big boy stuff, big girl stuff.

00:11:20.880 --> 00:11:22.490
This isn't little baby stuff I'm

00:11:22.500 --> 00:11:24.829
talking about; this is deep.

00:11:24.839 --> 00:11:27.889
This is going to the deep rivers.

00:11:27.899 --> 00:11:29.630
I'm trying to tell you all, there's

00:11:29.640 --> 00:11:31.190
a spirit on this you don't

00:11:31.200 --> 00:11:33.050
have a clue about. A lot of

00:11:33.050 --> 00:11:33.060
you

00:11:33.060 --> 00:11:36.230
are clueless about what goes on,

00:11:36.240 --> 00:11:38.030
even in the cults and the things

00:11:38.040 --> 00:11:41.990
they do.

00:11:42.000 --> 00:11:44.569
It's time for the body of Christ to grow

00:11:44.579 --> 00:11:47.990
up and start eating the meat. It's time

00:11:48.000 --> 00:11:50.509
for you to stop drinking the milk; you've

00:11:50.519 --> 00:11:52.850
been on the milk of the word

00:11:52.860 --> 00:11:55.430
too long. We've got to come up higher;

00:11:55.440 --> 00:11:57.470
we've got to come up and start grabbing

00:11:57.480 --> 00:11:59.690
hold of those T-bone steaks—or whatever,

00:11:59.700 --> 00:12:01.310
you may be vegan and that's your problem.

00:12:01.320 --> 00:12:03.710
Bite some lettuce if you're a vegan,

00:12:03.720 --> 00:12:05.990
or whatever.

00:12:06.000 --> 00:12:07.970
Let's just

00:12:07.980 --> 00:12:10.130
flow, y'all. Let's not get off on this

00:12:10.140 --> 00:12:12.050
petty stuff. But I'm going to tell you

00:12:12.060 --> 00:12:14.329
this: we can go into those rivers and,

00:12:14.339 --> 00:12:16.610
like I said, I

00:12:16.620 --> 00:12:18.530
could hear the people in Africa praying.

00:12:18.540 --> 00:12:20.030
I can hear the people in Asia praying.

00:12:20.040 --> 00:12:21.829
You can go in and out of those veins

00:12:21.839 --> 00:12:26.990
and you can pray with them.

00:12:27.000 --> 00:12:29.269
The body of Christ is so

00:12:29.279 --> 00:12:31.490
cool. The spirit realm is so cool, y'all.

00:12:31.500 --> 00:12:34.970
Number two: I was down and

00:12:34.980 --> 00:12:37.550
really having a hard time. I was

00:12:37.560 --> 00:12:39.290
at my mom and dad's church visiting,

00:12:41.210 --> 00:12:41.220
and

00:12:44.339 --> 00:12:46.730
I was worshiping. I was dealing with

00:12:46.740 --> 00:12:48.650
some

00:12:48.650 --> 00:12:48.660
heaviness—those

00:12:48.660 --> 00:12:50.150
forebodings I was telling you all

00:12:50.160 --> 00:12:51.829
about just a little bit ago.

00:12:51.839 --> 00:12:54.470
I was worshiping in their church, and

00:12:54.480 --> 00:12:56.569
all of a sudden there was a portal that

00:12:56.579 --> 00:12:59.629
opened up—a massive gateway. A portal

00:12:59.639 --> 00:13:02.329
opened up in

00:13:02.339 --> 00:13:05.829
the front of the church. I could see

00:13:05.839 --> 00:13:09.829
the ground;

00:13:09.839 --> 00:13:12.230
it was split where the portal

00:13:12.240 --> 00:13:13.850
was. There was a huge

00:13:13.850 --> 00:13:13.860
circular

00:13:13.860 --> 00:13:17.090
portal; it was purple and pink and

00:13:17.100 --> 00:13:19.009
all kinds of beautiful

00:13:19.019 --> 00:13:22.009
colors. It looked like cotton

00:13:22.019 --> 00:13:23.870
candy,

00:13:23.880 --> 00:13:26.690
like a Holy Ghost fog. It

00:13:26.700 --> 00:13:29.810
was beautiful. Jesus walks in with

00:13:29.820 --> 00:13:32.810
these angels—massive warring

00:13:32.820 --> 00:13:35.030
angels. This is the

00:13:35.040 --> 00:13:36.710
first time I've ever seen Jesus with

00:13:36.720 --> 00:13:39.949
angels like this. He walks in and

00:13:39.959 --> 00:13:43.009
stands before me.

00:13:43.009 --> 00:13:43.019
Behind

00:13:43.019 --> 00:13:45.590
where the portal was, it lifted up and I

00:13:45.590 --> 00:13:45.600
could see

00:13:45.600 --> 00:13:49.009
all these feet.

00:13:49.019 --> 00:13:51.110
They were barefoot;

00:13:51.120 --> 00:13:53.090
none of them had shoes on. I could

00:13:53.100 --> 00:13:54.829
see gowns and robes, again

00:13:54.829 --> 00:13:54.839
like

00:13:54.839 --> 00:13:56.870
what I told you I saw in

00:13:56.880 --> 00:14:00.170
heaven.

00:14:00.180 --> 00:14:02.509
I asked Jesus, 'What

00:14:02.519 --> 00:14:04.550
are all the feet?'and He said, 'That is

00:14:04.560 --> 00:14:07.670
part of the great cloud of witnesses, and

00:14:07.680 --> 00:14:09.829
they've come to watch the service and what's

00:14:09.839 --> 00:14:12.170
going on here right

00:14:12.170 --> 00:14:12.180
now.'I

00:14:12.180 --> 00:14:14.269
could hear them all talking.

00:14:14.279 --> 00:14:16.250
You know how when you get in a

00:14:16.260 --> 00:14:18.170
crowd you can't really understand what

00:14:18.180 --> 00:14:19.790
they're saying because when you hear a

00:14:19.800 --> 00:14:22.069
lot of voices together they're saying

00:14:22.069 --> 00:14:22.079
something—I

00:14:22.079 --> 00:14:24.170
could hear all the

00:14:24.180 --> 00:14:26.810
voices talking, but I couldn't make

00:14:26.820 --> 00:14:28.670
out what they were

00:14:28.680 --> 00:14:29.990
saying.

00:14:30.000 --> 00:14:31.850
There was

00:14:31.860 --> 00:14:34.370
activity going on in heaven, but they

00:14:34.380 --> 00:14:36.650
were watching.

00:14:36.660 --> 00:14:38.569
I could see their

00:14:38.579 --> 00:14:40.550
gowns and everything behind

00:14:40.560 --> 00:14:42.710
when Jesus opened up the portal. The

00:14:42.720 --> 00:14:45.530
portal lifted up and I could see in

00:14:45.530 --> 00:14:45.540
there—some

00:14:45.540 --> 00:14:47.329
trees

00:14:47.329 --> 00:14:47.339
and

00:14:47.339 --> 00:14:49.310
some stuff going on—but all I

00:14:49.320 --> 00:14:51.290
could see was from their feet to the

00:14:51.300 --> 00:14:53.449
middle of their waist.

00:14:53.459 --> 00:14:55.370
They were all lined up and

00:14:55.380 --> 00:14:57.889
looking from

00:14:57.899 --> 00:14:59.689
heaven into Earth at what was going on

00:14:59.699 --> 00:15:02.329
in the service.

00:15:05.579 --> 00:15:08.930
The

00:15:08.940 --> 00:15:11.329
King of Kings visited, and it was

00:15:11.339 --> 00:15:14.150
amazing; the

00:15:14.160 --> 00:15:17.090
glory was so thick. Jesus came up

00:15:17.100 --> 00:15:19.850
to me and

00:15:19.860 --> 00:15:21.889
stood right in

00:15:21.899 --> 00:15:23.810
front of me. It was in the spirit; it

00:15:23.820 --> 00:15:25.910
wasn't a full manifestation like flesh

00:15:25.920 --> 00:15:27.590
to flesh, like I had in my kitchen

00:15:27.600 --> 00:15:30.050
whenever He visited me that time. That

00:15:30.060 --> 00:15:31.850
was too intense; I

00:15:31.860 --> 00:15:33.949
collapsed. But I stood like this in the

00:15:33.959 --> 00:15:35.389
spirit realm and could see over in the

00:15:35.399 --> 00:15:38.329
spirit, and Jesus told me,

00:15:38.339 --> 00:15:41.990
'My yoke is easy and my burden is

00:15:42.000 --> 00:15:43.370
light, Brandon.

00:15:43.380 --> 00:15:45.590
You're thinking way too much.

00:15:45.600 --> 00:15:48.170
You're meditating

00:15:48.180 --> 00:15:50.329
on the wrong thoughts way too

00:15:50.329 --> 00:15:50.339
much.'He

00:15:50.339 --> 00:15:52.910
said, 'I want you

00:15:52.920 --> 00:15:55.730
to

00:15:55.740 --> 00:15:57.590
take the care out of your prayer.

00:15:57.600 --> 00:16:01.310
Be careful for nothing, son; you're

00:16:01.320 --> 00:16:03.470
full of

00:16:03.470 --> 00:16:03.480
care.'He

00:16:03.480 --> 00:16:05.990
said, 'Do you see

00:16:06.000 --> 00:16:09.650
this box?'I was inside a big wooden

00:16:09.660 --> 00:16:10.790
box

00:16:10.800 --> 00:16:13.910
and I was trying so hard to get out,

00:16:13.920 --> 00:16:16.430
but I believed I was

00:16:16.440 --> 00:16:18.650
in this box and that it had a lid on it

00:16:18.660 --> 00:16:20.930
and I was trapped.

00:16:24.959 --> 00:16:27.829
I was so bound by fear and

00:16:27.839 --> 00:16:30.290
torment all the time because of things I

00:16:30.300 --> 00:16:31.730
felt

00:16:31.740 --> 00:16:33.590
were going on in the world, in my family,

00:16:33.600 --> 00:16:35.530
and my house—a lot of

00:16:35.540 --> 00:16:37.550
occultist stuff. It was rough

00:16:37.560 --> 00:16:38.810
at that time.

00:16:41.100 --> 00:16:43.370
Jesus said, 'Brandon, there's

00:16:43.380 --> 00:16:46.189
no lid on the box. You're set free. All

00:16:46.199 --> 00:16:47.629
you've got to do is get out of the box.

00:16:47.639 --> 00:16:50.150
Your thoughts are

00:16:50.160 --> 00:16:52.370
why you're in the box. You're

00:16:52.380 --> 00:16:53.689
meditating on the

00:16:53.699 --> 00:16:55.550
wrong things. You need to start

00:16:55.560 --> 00:16:57.650
meditating on the right thing. Get in my

00:16:57.660 --> 00:17:00.110
word and meditate on my word.

00:17:00.120 --> 00:17:01.790
You're meditating too much on the news

00:17:01.790 --> 00:17:01.800
and

00:17:01.800 --> 00:17:03.769
these

00:17:03.779 --> 00:17:06.110
wrong things. My yoke is easy

00:17:06.120 --> 00:17:08.809
and my burden is light.'He told me,

00:17:10.860 --> 00:17:12.890
'You've got to stop thinking so much. You

00:17:12.900 --> 00:17:14.449
think way too much.'And He started

00:17:14.459 --> 00:17:16.610
laughing. Jesus started laughing at the

00:17:16.610 --> 00:17:16.620
circumstances.

00:17:16.620 --> 00:17:18.169
He said, 'Brandon, you've got to start

00:17:18.179 --> 00:17:20.150
laughing. You've got to start enjoying

00:17:20.150 --> 00:17:20.160
life.'He

00:17:20.160 --> 00:17:22.010
started laughing, and His

00:17:22.020 --> 00:17:24.169
laugh was so beautiful. It was so

00:17:24.179 --> 00:17:25.909
deep; He chuckled and laughed.

00:17:25.919 --> 00:17:27.829
He had beautiful, white, perfect

00:17:27.829 --> 00:17:27.839
straight

00:17:27.839 --> 00:17:30.110
teeth.

00:17:30.120 --> 00:17:31.789
He just laughed

00:17:31.789 --> 00:17:31.799
and

00:17:31.799 --> 00:17:34.070
was rejoicing, like, 'You've

00:17:34.070 --> 00:17:34.080
got

00:17:34.080 --> 00:17:37.130
to

00:17:37.130 --> 00:17:37.140
laugh!'I

00:17:37.140 --> 00:17:38.510
was fixed on His face.

00:17:38.520 --> 00:17:40.669
I'd

00:17:40.679 --> 00:17:42.590
never seen Jesus laugh like

00:17:42.600 --> 00:17:45.890
this. Everything has

00:17:45.900 --> 00:17:47.210
always been real serious when I've had

00:17:47.220 --> 00:17:48.950
these visitations,

00:17:48.950 --> 00:17:48.960
but

00:17:48.960 --> 00:17:50.150
this time He was

00:17:50.160 --> 00:17:51.470
laughing and telling me

00:17:51.480 --> 00:17:53.270
it's time to be full of joy.

00:17:53.280 --> 00:17:56.990
He said I had black smudges

00:17:57.000 --> 00:18:00.049
on my clothes and on me from all of

00:18:00.059 --> 00:18:02.110
the

00:18:02.120 --> 00:18:04.789
demonic pressure that I was allowing in

00:18:04.799 --> 00:18:06.890
my life by my thought life.

00:18:08.700 --> 00:18:09.890
I'm not going to tell you anything

00:18:09.900 --> 00:18:12.650
else He said because it's private, but He

00:18:12.660 --> 00:18:14.090
was just ministering to me.

00:18:14.100 --> 00:18:16.549
He lifted me up

00:18:16.559 --> 00:18:18.169
and showed me how to get out of that

00:18:18.179 --> 00:18:20.210
box and get in the word.

00:18:22.919 --> 00:18:25.909
The presence of God was

00:18:25.919 --> 00:18:28.130
so thick in that service that night.

00:18:30.120 --> 00:18:33.049
The power of God

00:18:33.059 --> 00:18:35.330
set me free, and I've never been the same

00:18:35.340 --> 00:18:37.669
since.

00:18:40.080 --> 00:18:42.409
These visitations

00:18:46.320 --> 00:18:48.529
have

00:18:53.700 --> 00:18:57.110
changed my life,

00:18:57.120 --> 00:18:58.669
and I've come to tell you these things

00:18:58.679 --> 00:19:01.190
because Jesus wants to change your life.

00:19:01.200 --> 00:19:03.710
He wants to love on you and tell you

00:19:03.720 --> 00:19:05.870
how much He loves you.

00:19:05.880 --> 00:19:08.270
I just wanted to

00:19:08.280 --> 00:19:10.430
encourage you all today that His yoke is easy and His burden

00:19:10.430 --> 00:19:10.440
is

00:19:10.440 --> 00:19:13.730
light.

00:19:13.740 --> 00:19:16.250
Don't walk in a spirit of heaviness; walk

00:19:16.260 --> 00:19:18.830
in a garment of praise. Be in that place

00:19:18.840 --> 00:19:21.590
of joy in your life because Jesus loves

00:19:21.600 --> 00:19:23.510
you so much.

00:19:23.520 --> 00:19:25.310
There's a great

00:19:25.320 --> 00:19:27.830
cloud of witnesses watching us,

00:19:27.840 --> 00:19:29.510
smiling and

00:19:29.520 --> 00:19:31.070
cheering us on.

00:19:40.080 --> 00:19:42.529
We have such a short amount of

00:19:42.539 --> 00:19:46.070
time before we get to go home.

00:19:46.080 --> 00:19:48.830
Jesus is coming, and I hope this

00:19:48.840 --> 00:19:50.630
blessed you today.

00:19:50.640 --> 00:19:53.270
Father, I

00:19:53.280 --> 00:19:55.490
thank You that You

00:19:55.500 --> 00:19:59.210
are bringing a spirit of peace and

00:19:59.220 --> 00:20:02.630
joy over their lives

00:20:02.640 --> 00:20:05.450
today. I thank You that

00:20:05.460 --> 00:20:08.150
there's a garment of praise. We give

00:20:08.160 --> 00:20:10.669
You that praise because You're worthy. We

00:20:10.679 --> 00:20:12.770
give You the honor and glory because You

00:20:12.780 --> 00:20:15.350
deserve every bit of it, Lord. You've

00:20:15.350 --> 00:20:15.360
cleansed

00:20:15.360 --> 00:20:17.029
us from all

00:20:17.039 --> 00:20:19.190
unrighteousness. You've taken away all the

00:20:19.200 --> 00:20:21.710
sin from our lives. You took the sickness

00:20:21.720 --> 00:20:24.289
and disease on your body. You took

00:20:24.299 --> 00:20:26.990
poverty for us, Father. I thank you. Mental

00:20:26.990 --> 00:20:27.000
torment—you

00:20:27.000 --> 00:20:28.850
took it. When they put

00:20:28.860 --> 00:20:31.010
that crown of thorns on your head, you

00:20:31.020 --> 00:20:33.529
took that on you, Father. You said that

00:20:33.539 --> 00:20:36.409
you took all those things; you became

00:20:36.419 --> 00:20:38.210
those things so that we don't have to go

00:20:38.220 --> 00:20:41.270
through them. What Jesus bore in his

00:20:41.280 --> 00:20:44.210
body, I need not bear in mine. I thank

00:20:44.220 --> 00:20:46.970
you, Father, that you've set me free by

00:20:46.980 --> 00:20:49.549
the blood of the lamb and by the

00:20:49.559 --> 00:20:52.010
word of my testimony. My testimony is

00:20:52.020 --> 00:20:54.890
great: Jesus Christ is my Lord and Savior.

00:20:54.900 --> 00:20:57.350
I thank you all for joining

00:20:57.360 --> 00:20:59.090
me today.

00:20:59.100 --> 00:21:01.610
I thank you all for being a part of

00:21:01.620 --> 00:21:03.169
this little community, my family

00:21:03.179 --> 00:21:06.470
here. I thank you. Please like my

00:21:06.480 --> 00:21:08.750
videos and share them; it really helps me

00:21:08.760 --> 00:21:11.150
with the algorithm. Put a smile on your

00:21:11.160 --> 00:21:13.490
face and a song in your heart. Jesus

00:21:13.500 --> 00:21:16.190
loves you so much, and we thank you for

00:21:16.200 --> 00:21:18.230
being a part of this family. God bless

00:21:18.240 --> 00:21:21.200
you all. Bye-bye.

